  lines:
  - Hello, you want to face me in your little game? (Space to continue)
  - My coins versus your coins? I'll wipe the floor with you.
  - 'So we''ll each flip 3 at once and compare the results?  '
  - "I will warn you...my coins aren't like other coins. \n(Press P at any time to
